                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.0144/169: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul at Chihuahua</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stewart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-09-08T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 8, 1919, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your September 5 noon reporting two American airplanes over city of Chihuahua.
                    War Department promises to issue strict orders against repetitions. Continue
                    your reports as heretofore.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
